Package nl.kb.xml.transformassert

Transform-assert is a small test library for XSLT transformations.
For a quick start tutorial with a few examples, please refer to the github README.

Package nl.kb.xml.transformassert Description

Transform-assert is a small test library for XSLT transformations.
For a quick start tutorial with a few examples, please refer to the github README.
To effectively walk through this documentation, start out at TransformAssert#describe(...) and follow the return references from each method.
